Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.10,0:00:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star,\NI want you to keep your room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've all had times\Nwhen you've done bad things{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.91,0:00:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}even though you knew\Nthey were wrong, haven't you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.85,0:00:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if you're sorry later and you\Napologize, everyone will understand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.23,0:00:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Yuri said a proper apology\Nfor his mistakes in the past,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and now he's one of our important comrades.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.65,0:00:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you know, it looks like there was also\Nsomething that happened way before that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Leon, Miss Sophie,\Nand the Angel's Maneuver...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What exactly happened\Nthree years ago? What? What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:01:02.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss hajimari wa aka to kuro no Passion{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:09.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Toki ni urahara na kokoro o tayori ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:16.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss kirifuda wa mirai o kaeru Mission{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:24.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koi ni aimai na kotae wa iranai {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:32.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arienai genjitsu minai furi shite mo Bet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:38.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Egatai shinjitsu\NCan U feel me now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:42.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nesshiyasui jibun ni Say What? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.31,0:01:46.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomadou iibun {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:55.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dreamin' samenai yume ochiteku sadame{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:02:02.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't stop lovin' Can't stop lovin' U\NYa ya ya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:10.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Believe in U hikikae ni subete ushinatte mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:17.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still lovin' Can't stop lovin' U\NNo no no{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:23.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.19,0:02:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time just kind of flew by, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of sad to think it's over, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.27,0:02:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up-ho! Up-ho! Up-ho! Up-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I'm begging you, can we stop now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, they like us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken, it's your time to shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.85,0:02:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:02:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Viva la France{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.23,0:03:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it great to see the\Naudience enjoying themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear the Kaleido Stage will\Nstart preparing to reopen soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that "huh"!\NI see you're as happy-go-lucky as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to return to\Nthe stage, then do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Something"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like blackmailing the Boss, for instance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That method is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I watched your Noir Circus show.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you've bounced back, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm sorry I caused\Nyou so much trouble, Mr. Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.52,0:03:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.81,0:03:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to Kaleido Stage too, Mr. Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Kalos asked me to return to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a producer and a performer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My my!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:03:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:03:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the only one who's returning to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.27,0:04:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Amazing Fated Duel."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can it be true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure hope so!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yuri said it, it has to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's totally okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Boss Boss Boss Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet! Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Um, I heard from\NMr. Yuri that you're let going me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,going me to let going\Nto let me back on stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.02,0:04:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm extending you a new contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play any role with all I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your role's already been decided, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.10,0:04:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You come in too, May.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be producing our next new show.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.56,0:04:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The program will be Swan Lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Odette, the lead, will be Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, she's accepting it meekly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:04:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she going to start making a fuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent my whole time in\NFrance researching "true stars."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You met a man named Alain, right Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he said he taught Sophie,\NMr. Leon's sister, the Angel's Maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he also say he'd tried to bring a true star
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into the world by perfecting\Nthe Angel's Maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the story from someone\Nwho knew Alain a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I too felt there was truth in the\Nthought that the Angel's Maneuver
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.81,0:05:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is connected to the path to being a true star.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I taught it to Sora for the Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that if it were true,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the hearts of the people who saw Sora's\NAngel's Maneuver should come together as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that didn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It did occur to me that perhaps\Nit wasn't the true star's maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when I met Alain in person,\NI was finally able to hear my answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:06:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we did wasn't the full Angel's Maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking about the\N"perfect Angel's Maneuver"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. There's another part\Nto the Angel's Maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, I'd like you to bring off a\Nperfect Angel's Maneuver on this stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll display the Angel's Maneuver\Nduring the climax of Swan Lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Sora, you get on that stage\Nand aim to be a true Kaleido Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A true Kaleido Star...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came back to be your partner in doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the reason you called me here was to\Ntell me you no longer had any use for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you can\Nteach the Angel's Maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying {\i1}you {\i0}can do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.85,0:06:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put it bluntly: that's impossible for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had high hopes for you,\Nthe man called the "God of Death,"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but from what I've seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're running from facing Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice but to\Nsay you're a disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Running, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been doing nothing\Nbut running, have you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you even walked away from the\NAngel's Maneuver training halfway through.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and do it, if you think you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}did {\i0}run. You really are a hopeless coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you can't even\Nget your revenge against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with these trapezes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen ones like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just the temporary\Nset for our rehearsals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to do the\NAngel's Maneuver on these?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.73,0:07:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder how they'll move... I can't even guess.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to try performing on these trapezes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.02,0:07:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.69,0:07:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Cathy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:08:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "what is it"? Do I look\Nlike I've come to sleep over or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... kind of do--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your guess is correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear about the plan for Swan Lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did, and I just couldn't sit still!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought, "Boy, I want to work\Nout this whole script with Mia!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how about it? Got an image?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I just now heard about it,\Nso I sort of haven't thought about it yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding! You say "just now,"\Nbut it's been almost an hour, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you could go this long
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without thinking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing's {\i0}come to mind yet? Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, would you like some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anything coming to--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For this show Ken's got his own job to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we can't rely on Ken's\Nairhead character anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barbara.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to think up some material, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll totally go over!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believed those words before,\Nand the reception was lukewarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's think about this more deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:08:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Miss Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a lot of trouble\Ninvestigating the Angel's Maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because there are very few\Nrecords of people who've attempted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's only natural, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It requires extraordinarily harsh\Ntraining, but it's not even flashy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone came to think that anyone\Nwho attempted such a thing was a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now there's hardly anybody\Nwho even knows what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.02,0:09:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you attempt the Angel's Maneuver and fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all that will be waiting\Nfor you is scornful laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you really walk this path?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're convinced this is the\Npath to being a true star, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's more like right now\NI just want to try my hand at this maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I think about what's going to happen\Nafterwards, it's not like I'll somehow know,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't want to not\Ndo it and then have regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents died when\NI was small, leaving me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they had all kinds\Nof things they wanted to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I think maybe dying really stung.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I live life trying everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I understand how much it stung Sophie that\Nshe couldn't bring off the Angel's Maneuver...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora. Do you know why Sophie died?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just before the Festival three years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.98,0:10:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I happened to see Leon and Sophie\Npracticing the Angel's Maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was something I could tell\Nwith one look wasn't perfected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't something that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:11:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,could possibly have jeopardized\NLayla's victory with the Golden Phoenix.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what I was afraid of then\Nwas Leon's presence in my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that if Kalos called Leon to\NKaleido Stage, my position would be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at the time I had ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had ambitions to rout out Kalos,\Nthe cause of my father's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and seize control of the Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the day of the Festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I called her to a park\Na ways off from the arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.98,0:11:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lied, telling her I had\Nsomething to say to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She kept waiting for me when\Nthere was no way I'd show up,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then at the last possible\Nmoment she tried to return to the arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.27,0:11:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On her way back, she was in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon called me countless\Ntimes from the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He asked me again and again to\Nmeet with her before she passed on,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:11:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,crying as he spoke the words.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophie is smitten with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell her you weren't trying to trick her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't let her die with a wounded heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you! {\i1}Please{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was almost my turn to perform; he must\Nhave known there was no way I'd come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... did something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can become a demon at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only a true demon can raise an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to try to become an angel,\Nyou'll have to accept a demon for a partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to settle things with Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whichever one of us can become\Na true demon will be your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri's Pisces and Leon's Scorpio...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.15,0:12:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The curtain is about to rise on a battle\Nmore fierce than any that has come before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.19,0:13:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time since\NSora's had a leading part, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.31,0:13:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now if only May weren't here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sora, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show May how much better you are than her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All finished already?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have that much stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great that you got to\Nhave your old room back, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Thanks for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like everybody's\Nexcited about your lead role.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm happy about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.44,0:13:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I wish they'd get along with May too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With May?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. After all, she is one of us,\Nperforming on the same stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's Mia and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there someone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Rosetta...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that might happen.\NIt's a good thing I came prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, okay. Come on in. Come all the way in...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You come too, Rosetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Come where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May, you don't have to come {\i1}that {\i0}far in...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll drink cola, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll do a comeback\Nparty and stuff with your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't go to things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're as dense as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying let's make a toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to have you show me\Nyour best Odette in this show.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to give the part of Odile my all,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that people will say she\Nshines more than Odette does.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you ever look like you're flagging,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm standing by ready\Nto steal your role anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Receiving Sagittarius' light,\NTaurus grows brighter as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, let's make a toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not really a toast, it's more like...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:14:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the way we do it in my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:15:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, shake shake shake shake shake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, for a second there I was \Nworried about whether I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally don't believe in this "stage with\Nno battles" thing you keep talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reality is, you won\Nagainst me and got the lead role.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to win against you someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way things work, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... But I don't feel like this is fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's because I've been\Nable to make friends with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you don't piss me off as\Nmuch as you did before, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you make friends\Nwith everyone else in the cast too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make friends with riffraff who\Nare all talk but don't do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all doing their best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.85,0:15:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to the stage again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me what your stage is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, practice starts tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.73,0:15:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed, you came\Ninstead of running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd give you a\Nchance to take your revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hate me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.81,0:16:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the man who caused Sophie's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then take that sword and face me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Can't you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't I reveal who\Nthe God of Death really is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no God of Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're not searching for a partner, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the past three years, you've\Njust been relieving your own mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,confirming over and over that\Nno one could take Sophie's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then Sora came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have noticed right away that\Nshe had abilities that rivaled Sophie's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gave Sora special\Ntraining out of the blue like that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because you thought if you gave her the\Ntest for the Angel's Maneuver she'd pass it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were hoping {\i1}Sora\N{\i0}would be the one to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sora never gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were afraid of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If things went on like that, the\NAngel's Maneuver training would continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd have to acknowledge that you're a\Ncoward who can't completely turn into a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.77,0:17:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason Sophie couldn't become an angel
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.15,0:17:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was because you couldn't\Ncompletely become a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.98,0:17:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you, those days while\NSophie's lukewarm training continued
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were more important than\Nher turning into an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that was the only way your\Ncowardice would remain undiscovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's most\Nrelieved that Sophie's dead, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:18:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you got by without\Nyour deceit being found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be grateful to me, Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I freed you from your suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophie's dream was a millstone\Naround your neck, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you say another word{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.77,0:18:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this time of night?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to settle things with Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whichever one of us can become\Na true demon will be your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.31,0:18:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophie might have realized your\Ntrue colors long before she died!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is fine. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm satisfied with this... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you'd\Nhurt each other on a stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter which one of\Nyou becomes my partner,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an Angel's Maneuver that can't be\Ncreated without doing things like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A maneuver like that is meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.35,0:20:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stage is grieving. Can't you tell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When fighting and hatred\Nhang over the stage, it grieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You say the same things as Sophie...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I promised her. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I promised I'd perfect the Angel's Maneuver\Nand make the "true star" a reality.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A true star will wreathe the stage in smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's hearts will come together as one...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The performers and the audience...\Nwill be like a family...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me, Leon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophie? Sophie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:21:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the truth is, I wasn't confident\Nthat a true star could really exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.73,0:21:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that "stage without battles"\Nthat Sophie dreamed of...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still couldn't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.44,0:21:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She left behind the promise alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora is the only one who\Ncan make good on that promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the only one who can raise\Nher to be an angel is you, Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.69,0:21:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time stopped for you three years ago\Nwhen Sophie died, and it hasn't moved since.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.23,0:21:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought if you could start moving by\Ngetting revenge on me, I'd gladly help, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did this on purpose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was doing it to atone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For what I did to Sophie,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.23,0:21:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and for what I did to Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.81,0:21:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.73,0:21:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.19,0:21:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You called me all the way over here for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't done anything to\Nme that you need to atone for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The value of the victory doesn't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know about Miss Sophie...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.31,0:22:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Yuri, just a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.98,0:22:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A stage without battles...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.27,0:22:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like Sophie was aiming to\Nbecome a true star without fighting anyone too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.02,0:22:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that that's possible,\Nbut there is one thing I've figured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.84,0:22:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something very important that\NI forgot to take care of before I left the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.60,0:22:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.15,0:22:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon will become Sora's partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you mean to make good on\Nyour promise, this is your last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.52,0:22:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
